             was indicted for <rs id="t18230219-101-off580" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18230219-101-off580" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18230219-101-off580" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18230219-101-cd581" type="crimeDate">8th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18230219-101-off580 t18230219-101-cd581"></join>, a coat, value 20 s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18230219-101-victim942" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
                     Hatton
                  <interp inst="t18230219-101-victim942" type="surname" value="Hatton"></interp>
